+# TextCaretInfoChangedDetails Object
+
+* `frame` [WebFrameMain](../web-frame-main.md) - The frame that owns the
+  focused editable element.
+* `url` string - The current URL of `frame`.
+* `isMainFrame` boolean - Whether `frame` is the main frame of the WebContents.
+* `inputType` string - The current Chromium text input type for the focused
+  editable context. Can be `text`, `password`, `search`, `email`, `number`,
+  `telephone`, `url`, `date`, `dateTime`, `dateTimeLocal`, `month`, `time`,
+  `week`, `textArea`, `contentEditable`, `dateTimeField`, `null`, or
+  `unknown`.
+* `inputMode` string - The current input mode requested by the focused editable
+  context. Can be `default`, `none`, `text`, `tel`, `url`, `email`, `numeric`,
+  `decimal`, `search`, or `unknown`.
+* `inputAction` string - The current enter-key action requested by the focused
+  editable context. Can be `default`, `enter`, `done`, `go`, `next`,
+  `previous`, `search`, `send`, or `unknown`.
+* `caret` [TextCaretInfoChangedDetailsCaret](text-caret-info-changed-details-caret.md) -
+  The current caret state.
+* `selection` [TextCaretInfoChangedDetailsSelection](text-caret-info-changed-details-selection.md) (optional) -
+  The current selection range reported for the focused editable context.
+* `composition` [TextCaretInfoChangedDetailsComposition](text-caret-info-changed-details-composition.md) -
+  The current IME composition state reported for the focused editable context.
+* `reason` string - Why Electron emitted this update. Can be `focus` or
+  `caret-move`.
